Package communication.messages.requests

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisconnectRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send DisconnectRequests to the server if the user wants to disconnect from the server
    EndRoundRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send EndRoundRequests to the server if the user wants to stop a turn with his character before the turn officially ends
    ExchangeInfinityStoneRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send ExchangeInfinityStoneRequests to the server if the user wants one of his characters to exchange an Infinity Stone with another character of his team
    MeleeAttackRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send MeleeAttackRequests to the server if the user wants to do an melee attack
    MoveRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send MoveRequests to the server if the user wants his character to move to another field
    PauseStartRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send PauseStartRequests to the server if the user wants to have a pause
    PauseStopRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send PauseStopRequests to the server if the user wants to end a pause
    RangedAttackRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send RangedAttackRequests to the server if the user wants to do an ranged attack
    Req
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send Reqs to the server if the user wants to receive the current GameState from the server
    UseInfinityStoneRequest
    Message-Class, which is responsible to send UseInfinityStoneRequests to the server if the user wants one of his characters to use his or her Infinity Stone
